      "span_text": "In this paper, we focus on translating into MRLs and issues associated with word formation on the target side. To provide a better translation we do not necessarily need a large target lexicon, as an MCW can be gradually formed during decoding by means of its subunits, similar to the solution proposed in character-based decoding models [CITATION_1] ."
